1 Demi Bantaa, Jaidyn Boully, and Mallory Miles, trainer Jenna Miller, and strength coach JD
2 McKinney; and
3 WHEREAS, the members of the championship team include Natalie Almand, Remie
4 Gautreau, Braidy Trabeau, Stella Allison, Kloe Parrish, Kenna Miles, Ava Acosta, Londyn
5 Crowder, Kendyl Ortego, Laney Wilson, Rilan Delaneuville, Genna McMorris, Grace
6 McMorris, Dani Delhommer, Taylor Aydell, and Raamiah Kennedy; and
7 WHEREAS, the dedication, sportsmanship, and teamwork demonstrated by the
8 French Settlement Lady Lions reflect great credit upon the players, coaches, faculty,
9 families, and the entire French Settlement community.
10 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
11 commend the French Settlement High School Lady Lions basketball team on winning the
12 2026 Louisiana High School Athletic Association Division III Non-Select state
13 championship and does hereby encourage the coaches and players to continue their excellent
14 work and always strive for greatness in competition.
15 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to
16 Principal John Chewning and Head Coach Jake Bourgeois.
